No. 109,

Orig.

Oklahoma et al. v. New Mexico.

Motion of the Special Master for compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and it is ordered that the Special Master is awarded a total of $64,112.96 for the period November 1, 1991, through September 23, 1992, to be paid equally by the parties. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 502 U. S. 1027.]
